    "TIMED_WALK_TEST_EXPLAINER_6_MIN_WALK" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This test measures your exercise capacity by tracking how far you walk in 6 minutes on a flat surface. (For reference ranges see [here](https://mhc-6mwts.streamlit.app).)\n\n**How to:** Find a flat, obstacle-free path. Wear comfortable shoes. Tap \"Start\" and walk at a steady, comfortably challenging pace to cover maximum distance. Keep your phone in your hand until it vibrates."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This test measures your exercise capacity by tracking how far you walk in 6 minutes on a flat surface. (For reference ranges see [here](https://mhc-6mwts.streamlit.app).)\n\n**How to:** Find a flat, obstacle-free path. Wear comfortable shoes. Tap \"Start\" and walk at a steady, comfortably challenging pace to cover maximum distance. Keep your phone in your hand until it vibrates."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esta prueba mide tu capacidad funcional de ejercicio al registrar la distancia que recorres caminando en 6 minutos sobre una superficie plana. (Para rangos de referencia, consulta [aquí](https://mhc-6mwts.streamlit.app).)\n\n**Cómo hacerlo:** Busqua un trayecto plano y libre de obstáculos. Usa calzado cómodo. Toqua \"Iniciar\" y camina a un ritmo constante que te resulte retador pero cómodo para cubrir la mayor distancia posible. Mantén tu teléfono en la mano hasta que vibre."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "TIMED_WALK_TEST_EXPLAINER_12_MIN_RUN" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This test estimates your aerobic fitness (VO2 max) by tracking how far you run in 12 minutes on a flat surface. (For reference ranges see [here](https://www.ptdirect.com/training-delivery/client-assessment/cooper-12-minute-run-a-predictive-test-of-vo2max).)\n\n**Warm-up:** Before beginning the test, perform about 10 minutes of light jogging to loosen your muscles and avoid injury. Catch your breath before proceeding.\n\n**How to:** Find a flat, obstacle-free path or running track. Wear comfortable running shoes. When you are ready, tap \"Start\" and run as fast as you possibly can to cover maximum distance until your phone vibrates. Keep your phone in your hand until it vibrates."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This test estimates your aerobic fitness (VO2 max) by tracking how far you run in 12 minutes on a flat surface. (For reference ranges see [here](https://www.ptdirect.com/training-delivery/client-assessment/cooper-12-minute-run-a-predictive-test-of-vo2max).)\n\n**Warm-up:** Before beginning the test, perform about 10 minutes of light jogging to loosen your muscles and avoid injury. Catch your breath before proceeding.\n\n**How to:** Find a flat, obstacle-free path or running track. Wear comfortable running shoes. When you are ready, tap \"Start\" and run as fast as you possibly can to cover maximum distance until your phone vibrates. Keep your phone in your hand until it vibrates."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esta prueba estima tu aptitud aeróbica (VO2 máx) al medir qué tan lejos corres en 12 minutos en una superficie plana. (Para rangos de referencia, consulta [aquí](https://www.ptdirect.com/training-delivery/client-assessment/cooper-12-minute-run-a-predictive-test-of-vo2max).)\n\n**Calentamiento:** Antes de comenzar la prueba, realiza 10 minutos de trote ligero para aflojar los músculos y evitar lesiones. Recupera el aliento antes de continuar.\n\n**Instrucciones:** Busca un camino plano y sin obstáculos o una pista de atletismo. Usa tenis para correr (zapatos deportivos). Cuando estés listo, toqua “Iniciar” y corre lo más rápido que puedas para cubrir la mayor distancia posible hasta que tu teléfono vibre. Mantén el teléfono en la mano hasta que vibre."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "TIMED_WALK_TEST_EXPLAINER_FOOTER" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Warning:** Stop immediately if you experience chest pain, severe shortness of breath, dizziness, or unusual fatigue."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Warning:** Stop immediately if you experience chest pain, severe shortness of breath, dizziness, or unusual fatigue."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Advertencia:** Detente de inmediato si presentas dolor en el pecho, falta de aire intensa, mareo o fatiga inusual."
          }
        }
      }
    },
